thread.title: Fiona

author: Fiona
title: Fiona
text:
Nelson Alexander Preston Peter was efficient, clear, gave good advice and used his people skills to run a successful campaign & auction.
Having sold a property 18months earlier with another real estate agent in the area I had experience in being able to compare the both & how they operated. I would highly recommend Nelson Alexander particularly Peter & Celeste.
